Package: PRmixer
Title: An R package to help assigning students as reviewers for peer review activities.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Florencia",
           family = "D'Andrea",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "florencia.dandrea@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0041-097X"))
Description: The package PeerReview Mixer (PRmixer) goal is to assign randomly students from one group as reviewers of another group. The function ` PRmixer::assign_reviewers()` considers that: (1) students cannot be assigned as reviewers of their same group, (2) all groups must have reviewers.
